gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 107, Pelicans 83
gameRecap.excerpt: The Thunder defeated the Pelicans, 107-83, as they win their fifth straight to improve to 32-13. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander led the Thunder with his league-leading 33rd 30-point game of the year (31 points, four rebounds, five assists) as Chet Holmgren added 20 points, 13 rebounds, and two blocks. Herbert Jones led the Pelicans with 14 points and 4 rebounds while Jonas Valanciunas added 14 points and nine rebounds. New Orleans moves to 26-19 with the loss.
